opic/New-Democracy |dead-url=no }}</ref><br>[[自由保守主義|自由保守主義]]<ref name="Nordsieck">{{Citation |first=Wolfram |last=Nordsieck |title=Greece |work=Parties and Elections in Europe |url=http://parties-and-elections.de/greece.html |accessdate=2012-03-15 |archive-date=2019-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622002602/http://parties-and-elections.de/greece.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Citation |first=Takis S. |last=Pappas |title=In Search of the Center: Conservative Parties, Electoral Competition, and Political Legitimacy in Southern Europe's New Democracies |work=Parties, Politics and Democracy in the New Southern Europe |publisher=The Johns Hopkins University Press |year=2001 |page=227 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=IT2VCWiYRCcC&pg=PA226&dq=new+democracy+greece+conservative&hl=en&sa=X&ei=BiZiT7a9FMyChQeImJW0CA&ved=0CF4Q6AEwBzgK#v=snippet&q=nea%20demokratia%20conservative&f=false |accessdate=2012-05-08 |archive-date=2019-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211120810/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=IT2VCWiYRCcC&pg=PA226&dq=new+democracy+greece+conservative&hl=en&sa=X&ei=BiZiT7a9FMyChQeImJW0CA&ved=0CF4Q6AEwBzgK#v=snippet&q=nea%20demokratia%20conservative&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><br>[[基督教民主主義|基督教民主主義]]<ref name="Nordsieck"/><br>[[右翼民粹主义|右翼民粹主义]]<ref>* https://www.humanite.fr/grece-kyriakos-mitsotakis-recycle-les-voix-de-lextreme-droite-674668 {{Wayback|url=https://www.humanite.fr/grece-kyriakos-mitsotakis-recycle-les-voix-de-lextreme-droite-674668 |date=20211009183210 }} Grèce. Kyriakos Mitsotakis recycle les voix de l’extrême droite]
